query:
SELECT l.id, l.nome
FROM gestor_lojas gl
JOIN lojas l ON l.id = gl.lojaId
JOIN gestores g ON g.id = gl.gestorId
JOIN users u ON u.id = g.userId
WHERE u.name LIKE '%Fabio%'
ORDER BY l.nome;
